<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Helios Astro — Dieu est la lumière</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #06070b;
      --bg-soft: #0d1018;
      --card: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      --line: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      --gold: #d7b56d;
      --gold-2: #f0d79a;
      --text: #f5f2ea;
      --muted: #b8b0a2;
      --violet: #7f6bff;
      --blue: #56b9ff;
      --rose: #f06ab4;
      --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.45);
      --radius: 24px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(127,107,255,.16), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 30%, rgba(86,185,255,.14), transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 80%, rgba(240,106,180,.12), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #06070b 0%, #090c13 38%, #05060a 100%);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .noise,
    .orb,
    .starfield,
    .sacred-bg { pointer-events: none; }

    .starfield {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(2px 2px at 20px 30px, rgba(255,255,255,.65), transparent),
        radial-gradient(2px 2px at 40px 70px, rgba(255,255,255,.4), transparent),
        radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 50px 160px, rgba(255,255,255,.45), transparent),
        radial-gradient(2px 2px at 90px 40px, rgba(255,255,255,.3), transparent),
        radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 130px 80px, rgba(255,255,255,.45), transparent);
      background-size: 180px 180px;
      opacity: .18;
      z-index: 0;
      animation: drift 28s linear infinite;
    }

    @keyframes drift {
      from { transform: translateY(0); }
      to { transform: translateY(-180px); }
    }

    .orb {
      position: fixed;
      border-radius: 999px;
      filter: blur(70px);
      opacity: .22;
      z-index: 0;
      animation: float 10s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .orb.one {
      width: 320px; height: 320px;
      background: rgba(127,107,255,.45);
      top: 8%; left: -60px;
    }
    .orb.two {
      width: 360px; height: 360px;
      background: rgba(86,185,255,.34);
      top: 38%; right: -80px;
      animation-delay: -3s;
    }
    .orb.three {
      width: 260px; height: 260px;
      background: rgba(240,106,180,.28);
      bottom: 4%; left: 12%;
      animation-delay: -6s;
    }

    @keyframes float {
      0%,100% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-18px) translateX(10px); }
    }

    .container {
      width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      background: rgba(6,7,11,.58);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 16px 0;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: .92rem;
    }

    .logo {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(240,215,154,.15), rgba(215,181,109,.08));
      border: 1px solid rgba(215,181,109,.35);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 18px rgba(240,215,154,.12), 0 0 22px rgba(215,181,109,.12);
    }

    .logo svg { width: 26px; height: 26px; }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: .95rem;
      transition: .25s ease;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    .btn,
    .btn-secondary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      min-height: 50px;
      padding: 0 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: transform .22s ease, box-shadow .22s ease, background .22s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
    }

    .btn {
      color: #111;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold-2), var(--gold));
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(215,181,109,.28);
    }

    .btn:hover,
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      color: var(--text);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.12);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 72px 0 48px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr .9fr;
      gap: 38px;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 78px);
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(215,181,109,.22);
      background: rgba(215,181,109,.08);
      color: var(--gold-2);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      font-size: .84rem;
      letter-spacing: .05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5vw, 5.6rem);
      line-height: .95;
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      letter-spacing: -.04em;
    }

    .gradient-text {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff7df 0%, var(--gold-2) 30%, #fff 55%, #c9d6ff 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
    }

    .hero p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      line-height: 1.72;
      max-width: 640px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 28px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .hero-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 28px;
      max-width: 720px;
    }

    .stat {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .stat strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .stat span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .92rem;
    }

    .book-wrap {
      position: relative;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      min-height: 620px;
    }

    .sacred-bg {
      position: absolute;
      width: min(640px, 100%);
      aspect-ratio: 1;
      opacity: .65;
      animation: spin 48s linear infinite;
    }

    .sacred-bg svg {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 16px rgba(215,181,109,.22));
    }

    @keyframes spin {
      from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
      to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
    }

    .book {
      position: relative;
      width: min(390px, 78vw);
      aspect-ratio: 0.69;
      border-radius: 28px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(8,9,12,.12), rgba(8,9,12,.5)),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 22%, rgba(255,244,214,.18), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(145deg, #0d111b, #05070c 60%, #0f1220 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      box-shadow: 0 30px 90px rgba(0,0,0,.55), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.04) inset;
      transform: perspective(1300px) rotateY(-11deg) rotateX(5deg);
      animation: levitate 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes levitate {
      0%,100% { transform: perspective(1300px) rotateY(-11deg) rotateX(5deg) translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: perspective(1300px) rotateY(-9deg) rotateX(4deg) translateY(-10px); }
    }

    .book::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at center, transparent 0 13%, rgba(215,181,109,.36) 13.4%, transparent 13.8%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, transparent 0 22%, rgba(215,181,109,.26) 22.4%, transparent 22.8%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, transparent 0 31%, rgba(215,181,109,.20) 31.4%, transparent 31.8%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, transparent 0 40%, rgba(215,181,109,.15) 40.4%, transparent 40.8%);
      opacity: .85;
    }

    .book::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 18px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(215,181,109,.18);
    }

    .book-inner {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 34px 28px;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .book-kicker {
      color: var(--gold-2);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .18em;
      font-size: .78rem;
    }

    .book-title {
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
      line-height: .95;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .book-sub {
      color: #ddd2bf;
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-size: .97rem;
      max-width: 260px;
    }

    .book-author {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      gap: 12px;
      color: #d9d1c3;
      font-size: .88rem;
      letter-spacing: .06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 40px 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0 auto 28px;
    }

    .section-title h2 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
      letter-spacing: -.03em;
    }

    .section-title p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
    }

    .grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .card {
      position: relative;
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.06), rgba(255,255,255,.04));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: -30%;
      right: -20%;
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(215,181,109,.18), transparent 65%);
    }

    .icon {
      width: 56px;
      height: 56px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(215,181,109,.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(215,181,109,.18);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: var(--gold-2);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .card p,
    .card li { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; }

    .split {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 22px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .list {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .list li { margin-bottom: 12px; }

    .quote-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .quote {
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .quote p {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #ece6dc;
    }

    .quote strong {
      font-size: .95rem;
      color: var(--gold-2);
    }

    .pricing {
      padding: 28px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.08), rgba(255,255,255,.04)),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(215,181,109,.18), transparent 35%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(215,181,109,.24);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .pricing .price {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 10px 0 16px;
    }

    .pricing .price strong {
      font-size: 3rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .pricing .price span {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .mini-note {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .92rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .cta-box {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 34px;
      border-radius: 32px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(215,181,109,.12), rgba(127,107,255,.14) 55%, rgba(86,185,255,.12)),
        rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cta-box h2 { margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem); }
    .cta-box p { margin: 0 auto 22px; max-width: 760px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8; }

    footer {
      padding: 34px 0 56px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
      font-size: .95rem;
    }

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(24px);
      transition: opacity .7s ease, transform .7s ease;
    }

    .reveal.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero,
      .split,
      .grid-3,
      .quote-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .hero { padding-top: 44px; }
      .book-wrap { min-height: 460px; order: -1; }
      .hero-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .nav { align-items: flex-start; }
      .nav-links { justify-content: flex-end; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .container { width: min(100% - 20px, 1180px); }
      .nav { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
      .nav-links { justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; }
      .hero-actions { flex-direction: column; }
      .btn, .btn-secondary { width: 100%; }
      .card, .quote, .pricing, .cta-box { padding: 20px; }
      .book { width: min(320px, 88vw); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="starfield"></div>
  <div class="orb one"></div>
  <div class="orb two"></div>
  <div class="orb three"></div>

  <header>
    <div class="container nav">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="logo" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none">
            <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="26" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" opacity=".9"/>
            <circle cx="50" cy="24" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" opacity=".7"/>
            <circle cx="72" cy="37" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" opacity=".7"/>
            <circle cx="72" cy="63" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" opacity=".7"/>
            <circle cx="50" cy="76" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" opacity=".7"/>
            <circle cx="28" cy="63" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" opacity=".7"/>
            <circle cx="28" cy="37" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" opacity=".7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span>Helios Astro</span>
      </div>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="#livre">Le livre</a>
        <a href="#contenu">Contenu</a>
        <a href="#avis">Avis</a>
        <a href="#acheter">Acheter</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="container hero">
      <div class="reveal visible">
        <div class="eyebrow">Livre • Géométrie sacrée • Lumière • Conscience</div>
        <h1><span class="gradient-text">Dieu est la lumière</span><br>La géométrie sacrée révélée</h1>
        <p>
          Une page de vente premium conçue pour transformer ton univers visuel en machine de conversion.
          Elle met en scène le livre, structure le message, valorise la promesse et pousse naturellement à l’achat.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="btn" href="#acheter">Acheter maintenant</a>
          <a class="btn-secondary" href="#contenu">Voir le contenu</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <strong>Positionnement</strong>
            <span>Spirituel, visuel, différenciant, mémorable.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <strong>Conversion</strong>
            <span>Structure claire : intrigue, preuve, désir, action.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <strong>Intégration</strong>
            <span>Prête à brancher sur HeliosAstro et PayPal.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="book-wrap reveal">
        <div class="sacred-bg" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 600 600" fill="none">
            <g stroke="rgba(215,181,109,.42)" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="300" cy="300" r="50"/>
              <circle cx="300" cy="200" r="50"/>
              <circle cx="386.6" cy="250" r="50"/>
              <circle cx="386.6" cy="350" r="50"/>
              <circle cx="300" cy="400" r="50"/>
              <circle cx="213.4" cy="350" r="50"/>
              <circle cx="213.4" cy="250" r="50"/>
              <circle cx="300" cy="100" r="50"/>
              <circle cx="473.2" cy="200" r="50"/>
              <circle cx="473.2" cy="400" r="50"/>
              <circle cx="300" cy="500" r="50"/>
              <circle cx="126.8" cy="400" r="50"/>
              <circle cx="126.8" cy="200" r="50"/>
              <circle cx="300" cy="300" r="150" opacity=".5"/>
              <circle cx="300" cy="300" r="250" opacity=".28"/>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="book" id="livre">
          <div class="book-inner">
            <div>
              <div class="book-kicker">Helios Astro</div>
              <h2 class="book-title">Dieu est<br>la lumière</h2>
              <p class="book-sub">La fleur de vie, le grand secret de l’univers. Une oeuvre à la croisée de la spiritualité, de la structure et de la vision.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="book-author">
              <span>Thierry Tafani</span>
              <span>Atefeh Ghasemiyan</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title reveal">
          <h2>Une landing page qui parle enfin le langage de ton livre</h2>
          <p>
            Pas une page fade avec trois paragraphes et un bouton perdu au milieu. Ici, on vend un univers.
            Lumière, géométrie sacrée, profondeur visuelle, crédibilité éditoriale et appel à l’action net.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-3">
          <article class="card reveal">
            <div class="icon">✦</div>
            <h3>Impact immédiat</h3>
            <p>Le visiteur comprend en quelques secondes qu’il ne s’agit pas d’un simple livre, mais d’une vision structurée et singulière.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card reveal">
            <div class="icon">◎</div>
            <h3>Univers cohérent</h3>
            <p>Couleurs, atmosphère, rythme visuel et vocabulaire sont alignés avec l’ADN Helios Astro.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card reveal">
            <div class="icon">↗</div>
            <h3>Orientation vente</h3>
            <p>Chaque section pousse vers l’achat : valeur, contenu, preuve sociale, offre et bouton final sans ambiguïté.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="contenu">
      <div class="container split">
        <article class="card reveal">
          <h3>Ce que découvre le lecteur</h3>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Le lien entre lumière, structure, matière et conscience.</li>
            <li>Une lecture visuelle de la fleur de vie et de la géométrie sacrée.</li>
            <li>Une traversée entre microcosme, corps humain, macrocosme et spiritualité.</li>
            <li>Un ouvrage atypique, à la fois contemplatif, symbolique et argumenté.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="pricing reveal" id="acheter">
          <div class="eyebrow">Offre mise en avant</div>
          <h3>Édition premium</h3>
          <div class="price">
            <strong>24€</strong>
            <span>couverture mate</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mini-note">
            Remplace ce bloc par ton prix réel, ton bouton PayPal ou ton lien de paiement. La structure est déjà prête.
          </p>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Livre imprimé haute qualité</li>
            <li>Visuels forts et univers propriétaire</li>
            <li>Positionnement unique sur la géométrie sacrée</li>
          </ul>
          <div style="margin-top:20px; display:flex; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a class="btn" href="#">Acheter via PayPal</a>
            <a class="btn-secondary" href="#avis">Lire les avis</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="avis">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title reveal">
          <h2>La preuve sociale fait le travail lourd</h2>
          <p>
            Remplace ces textes par de vrais retours lecteurs, avis Amazon, captures ou citations presse. Le cadre est prêt.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="quote-grid">
          <blockquote class="quote reveal">
            <p>« Une oeuvre visuellement forte, qui propose une lecture ambitieuse de l’univers et de la lumière. »</p>
            <strong>Lecteur • édition spirituelle</strong>
          </blockquote>
          <blockquote class="quote reveal">
            <p>« L’univers graphique capte immédiatement. On sent une vraie signature, pas un produit générique. »</p>
            <strong>Lectrice • art symbolique</strong>
